Package FOODIE

Class Branch

Object
Branch
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Branch extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a branch of the restaurant. Each branch has a menu, name, ArrayList of Staff, Manager and Order.

  • Method Details

    • getQuota

      public int getQuota()
      Calculates quota of managers in a branch Quota = 1 if staff less than or equal to 4, quota = 2 if staff less than or equal to 8, quota = 3 if staff less than or equal to 15
      Returns:
      returns quota of managers based on number of staff

    • addStaff

      public void addStaff(Staff staff)
      Adds a staff to the branch object. If staff is a Manager, check that quota is not hit before adding to managers ArrayList. If staff is a Staff, add the Staff object to the Branch staffs ArrayList
      Parameters:
      staff - Staff to be added to the branch.

    • removeStaff

      public void removeStaff(Staff staff)
      Removes a staff from the branch object. Method first checks that staff is a Manager or Staff, before removing from relevant ArrayList.
      Parameters:
      staff - Staff to be removed from branch.
